14-15 August Date Cookies

1 cup soft butter
1/2 cup sugar
2 cup flour
1/4 teaspoon salt
2 teaspoon vanilla
1 lb coconut
1 lb pitted dates

Cream butter, sugar, vanilla, add flour and salt. Mix well and shape into egg shaped rounds, putting the date in the middle. Surround date with cookie dough. Then roll in coconut and bake at 325F for about 20 minutes.